{"tid":1383317,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"官斥警方案件主管處事粗疏浪費法庭時間","createTime":"2019-07-29T16:14:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T16:18:34.000Z","uid":286952,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"afefe2052a897e52e30250687f3a417200e47dbe","tid":1383317,"uid":286952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:14:36.000Z","msg":"名列前茅、對物理化學有濃厚興趣的16歲中四男生，被揭發在家藏有電槍、彈匣及胡椒噴霧等武器，今在東區裁判法院認罪。惟控方承認無證據顯示有關武器用作犯法、損害社會或傷人用途。裁判官要求控方再尋求法律意見，以考慮會否用另一種方式處理本案，案件下月6日再訊。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">官怒斥案件主管：「你係認真咁做嘢？」</span></span></strong><br />\n被告今早認罪後，署理總裁判官羅德泉欲審視控方提交的武器化驗報告，卻發現報告沒有撮要。羅官隨即透過主控官追問案件主管謂：「你係認真咁做嘢？就咁將一疊嘢放上嚟。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>你係做嘢？咁粗疏﹗</strong></span>」羅官更將整疊文件<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>用力擲到枱面</strong></span>，問：「<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">龍幫辦，係咪啊？</span></strong>」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iAMVmUo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiAMVmUo.png&h=41631c16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190729&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59875937\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190729%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59875937&d=BhuSHdI33QWLqsaIYsxmJSMX%2BuEjOoKUanh%2Bi4Xf2cM%3D&h=d7b5ba7e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190729%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59875937&h=18c85c4d\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190729&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59875937</a> (2019年07月29)"},{"pid":"2258e3524c8c526c1868a56e621d47f2fd29ff9a","tid":1383317,"uid":286952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:15:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" c